						<summary>

						<p>This inscription mentions the names of some lamp-bearers, Ādivarāhappichchar, Vellaippaṉṟipichar, etc., inthe temple of Āḻvār at Tirumuṭṭam, who received some gift from Sriramaṉ Paramēshvara bhaṭṭaṉ and also mentions the name of the village Sri Tribhuvana Mahādēvichchēri eḻilūr in SrīVīranārāyana Chatūrvēdimaṅgalam.</p>						

						</summary>
