<p>
<lb n="1"/>k<hi rend="grantha">ra</hi>macoḻa tevaṟku yāṇṭu Eṭṭāvatu tirumuṭṭat tāḻvār ko
<lb n="2"/>yililt tiruviḷakkup piccakaḷil Ātivarākap piccarum tiruviḷakkup
<lb n="3"/>piccarum veḷḷaippanṟippiccarum Uḷḷiṭṭār vacam <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> viranārāyaṇa[ <hi rend="grantha">cca</hi>tu]
<lb n="4"/><hi rend="grantha">rvve</hi>ti maṅkalattu <hi rend="grantha">śrī tribhu</hi>vana <hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi>vicceri Eḻilūr niya
<lb n="5"/>ṟuc cirāman <hi rend="grantha">para</hi>me<hi rend="grantha">śvara bha</hi>ṭṭa<hi rend="grantha">soma</hi>yā<hi rend="grantha">ji</hi>yār <hi rend="grantha">brahma</hi>ṇiyār ti
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kuccāniyār Ivar makaṉ Ārāvamutuccāriyārum Ivar taṅkai
</p>

